{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"direction","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/direction","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">CSS 属性&nbsp;<strong><code>direction</code></strong>&nbsp;用来设置文本、表列水平溢出的方向。&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>rtl</code>&nbsp;表示从右到左&nbsp;(类似希伯来语或阿拉伯语)，&nbsp;<code>ltr</code>&nbsp;表示从左到右&nbsp;(类似英语等大部分语言).</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/css/direction.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n\n\n<p>值得注意的是文本方向通常由文档定义&nbsp;(e.g., with <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/dir\">HTML's <code>dir</code> attribute</a>) 而不是通过直接使用&nbsp;<code>direction</code>&nbsp;属性定义。</p>\n\n<p>该属性设置可以设置块级元素文本的基本方向，也可以设置由通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a>属性创建的嵌入元素的方向。与此同时，它还可以设置文本、块级元素的默认对齐方式&nbsp;，以及表行中的单元格的流动方向。</p>\n\n<p>与 HTML 中的 <code>dir</code>&nbsp;属性不同，<code>direction</code>属性不会从表列继承到表单元格，因为 CSS 继承遵从文档流，而表单元格位于行内部，但不在列内部。</p>\n\n<p><code>direction</code>&nbsp;属性和&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a> 属性不受 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/all\"><code>all</code></a>&nbsp;属性影响。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:css no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* Keyword values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ltr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> rtl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Global values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"取值","title":"取值","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"ltr\"><code>ltr</code></dt>\n <dd>默认属性。可设置文本和其他元素的默认方向是从左到右。</dd>\n <dt id=\"rtl\"><code>rtl</code></dt>\n <dd>可设置文本和其他元素的默认方向是从右到左。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"标准语法","title":"标准语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">ltr <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> rtl</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">blockquote</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> rtl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-writing-modes/#direction","title":"CSS Writing Modes Level 4"}],"query":"css.properties.direction"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">初始值</a></th><td><code>ltr</code></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">适用元素</th><td>all elements</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">是否是继承属性</a></th><td>yes</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">计算值</a></th><td>as specified</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>discrete</td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.direction","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/direction/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect5\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/writing-mode\"><code>writing-mode</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"值得注意的是文本方向通常由文档定义 (e.g., with HTML's dir attribute) 而不是通过直接使用 direction 属性定义。","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"direction","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"direction","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"direction","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"direction","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"direction","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"direction","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"direction","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/css/direction","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/css/direction/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS（层叠样式表）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/direction","title":"direction"}],"pageTitle":"direction - CSS（层叠样式表） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}